          <title>
            <string language="en">Lonely mountains: The monadnocks of the inner Piedmont</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Einsame Berge: Die monadnocks des inneren 
Piedmonts</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Montagnes isolées : Les monadnocks du 
Piémont intérieur</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Montanhas sós: Os monadnocks do Piedmont 
interno</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Montagne sole: I monadnocks del Piemonte 
interno</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Μόνα βουνά: Τα monadnocks εσωτερικό 
piedmont</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Montañas solas: Los monadnocks del Piedmont
interno</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">This Carolina Environmental Diversity Explorations "virtual field trip" explores the geology of North Carolina's monadnocks, mountains that rise individually above the surrounding topography.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Science and Technology</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Dieses Carolina virtuellen, welches die 
Klimaverschiedenartigkeit-Erforschungen "Reise" auffangen, 
erforscht die Geologie von monadnocks Nord-Carolina, Berge, die 
einzeln über die umgebende Topographie steigen.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les explorations environnementales "voyage de 
cette diversité de la Caroline de zone virtuel" explore la géologie 
des monadnocks du nord de la Caroline, les montagnes qui se 
lèvent individuellement au-dessus de la topographie environnante.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">As explorações ambientais "desengate desta 
diversidade de Carolina de campo virtual" exploram a geologia de 
monadnocks de North.carolina, as montanhas que se levantam 
individualmente acima do topography circunvizinho.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Le esplorazioni ambientali "viaggio di questa 
diversità della Carolina di campo virtuale" esplora la geologia dei 
monadnocks del North.carolina, montagne che aumentano individualmente 
sopra la topografia circostante.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Εξερευνήσεις "εικονικό ταξίδι αυτής της 
ποικιλομορφίας της Καρολίνας οι περιβαλλοντικές πεδίων" ερευνούν 
τη γεωλογία της βόρειας Καρολίνας monadnocks, βουνά που 
αυξάνονται χωριστά επάνω από την περιβάλλουσα τοπογραφία.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Las exploraciones ambientales "disparo al campo de
esta diversidad de Carolina virtual" exploran la geología de los 
monadnocks de Carolina del Norte, las montañas que se levantan 
individualmente sobre la topografía circundante.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Wissenschaft und Technologie</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">La Science et technologie</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Ciência e tecnologia</string>
          </keyword>
